SELECT SUM(IFNULL(m_visits,0)) as summe_${webColor}
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.total_visits`
WHERE site_level2 = "ndr.de" AND
${web_redaktionen:doublequote} = page_chapter1 AND
${Unterkapitel:doublequote} = page_chapter2 AND
"Alle Sendungs-ID" = sendungs_id 
AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr

WITH vid_sum AS(
SELECT 
  SUM(COALESCE(m_av_playbacks,0)) as summeVideo
FROM 
  `Piano.av`
WHERE 
site_level2 = "ndr.de" AND
"$web_redaktionen" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter1_tags) AND
"$Unterkapitel" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter2_tags)
AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" IN UNNEST(sendungs_id_tags)
AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
AND av_content_type = "Video" 
),
audio_sum as(SELECT 
  SUM(COALESCE(m_av_playbacks,0)) as summeAudio
FROM 
  `Piano.av`
WHERE 
site_level2 = "ndr.de" AND
"$web_redaktionen" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter1_tags) AND
"$Unterkapitel" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter2_tags)
AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" IN UNNEST(sendungs_id_tags)
AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
AND av_content_type = "Audio")
SELECT
  (summeVideo + summeAudio) as summe_${webColor}
FROM
  vid_sum, audio_sum as relative_sum
-- OR 
-- AND 
-- av_content_type ="Audio"

SELECT SUM(page_impressions_unique) as current_value
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.facebookInsights`
WHERE profileId = ${profile_ID_FB}
AND EXTRACT(MONTH from time) = $Monat 
AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr

with impressions_by_day_new as (
	SELECT
    sum(sum_impression_day) as sum_impressions, count(n_day) as num_days, avg(ID) as ID
    FROM(
	SELECT sum(page_impressions_unique) as sum_impression_day, extract(DAY from time) as n_day, avg(profileID) as ID
	  FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.facebookInsights`
    WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH from time) = $Monat 
    AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr 
		AND profileID = $profile_ID_FB
    GROUP BY n_day)
),
potential_reach as (
select ROUND((impressions_by_day_new.sum_impressions/impressions_by_day_new.num_days),3) as avg_impressions_new, impressions_by_day_new.ID as ID
FROM impressions_by_day_new
)
SELECT avg_impressions_new as reach  from potential_reach

SELECT followers as page_follows
		FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.instagram`
		WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH from time) = $Monat 
		AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr 
		AND profileID = $profile_ID_INSTA

IF $profile_ID_INSTA = 0 THEN
SELECT
  "N/A";
ELSE
SELECT
  CONCAT(
    REPEAT(
      " ",
      5 - CHAR_LENGTH(CAST(totalInteractions as STRING))
    ),
    REPLACE(
      CAST(
        FORMAT(
          "%'.0f",
          CAST(ROUND(totalInteractions) as NUMERIC)
        ) AS STRING
      ),
      ",",
      "."
    )
  ) totalInteractions
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      ROUND(
        SUM(
          CASE
            WHEN type = 'Reel' THEN IFNULL(totalInteractions, 0)
            ELSE IFNULL(engagement, 0)
          END
        ) / (CASE
					WHEN CURRENT_DATE() < DATE_ADD(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 7), INTERVAL 1 MONTH) THEN DATE_DIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),DATE($Jahr, $Monat,1),DAY)+1
					ELSE DATE_DIFF( LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), MONTH), DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), DAY ) + 1
				END),
        0
      ) AS totalInteractions
    FROM
      `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.instagramInsightsOwnPosts`
    WHERE
      profileId = $profile_ID_INSTA
      AND EXTRACT(
        MONTH
        from
          time
      ) = $Monat
      AND EXTRACT(
        YEAR
        from
          time
      ) = $Jahr
  );
END IF;

WITH past_value as(
  SELECT
    SUM(IFNULL(m_visits, 0)) as past_sum
  FROM
    `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.total_visits`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND ${web_redaktionen:doublequote} = page_chapter1
    AND ${Unterkapitel:doublequote} = page_chapter2
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" = sendungs_id
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
),
current_value AS (
  SELECT
    SUM(IFNULL(m_visits, 0)) as current_sum
  FROM
    `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.total_visits`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND ${web_redaktionen:doublequote} = page_chapter1
    AND ${Unterkapitel:doublequote} = page_chapter2
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" = sendungs_id
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = $Monat
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = $Jahr
)
SELECT
  ((current_sum - past_sum) / past_sum) * 100 as summe_${webColor}
FROM
  current_value, past_value as relative_difference

WITH vid_sum_current AS(
  SELECT
    SUM(COALESCE(m_av_playbacks, 0)) as summeVideoCurrent
  FROM
    `Piano.av`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND "$web_redaktionen" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter1_tags)
    AND "$Unterkapitel" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter2_tags)
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" IN UNNEST(sendungs_id_tags)
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = $Monat
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = $Jahr
    AND av_content_type = "Video"
),
vid_sum_past AS(
  SELECT
    SUM(COALESCE(m_av_playbacks, 0)) as summeVideoPast
  FROM
    `Piano.av`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND "$web_redaktionen" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter1_tags)
    AND "$Unterkapitel" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter2_tags)
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" IN UNNEST(sendungs_id_tags)
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
    AND av_content_type = "Video"
),
audio_sum_current as(
  SELECT
    SUM(COALESCE(m_av_playbacks, 0)) as summeAudioCurrent
  FROM
    `Piano.av`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND "$web_redaktionen" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter1_tags)
    AND "$Unterkapitel" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter2_tags)
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" IN UNNEST(sendungs_id_tags)
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = $Monat
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = $Jahr
    AND av_content_type = "Audio"
),
audio_sum_past as(
  SELECT
    SUM(COALESCE(m_av_playbacks, 0)) as summeAudioPast
  FROM
    `Piano.av`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND "$web_redaktionen" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter1_tags)
    AND "$Unterkapitel" IN UNNEST(bi_av_page_chapter2_tags)
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" IN UNNEST(sendungs_id_tags)
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
    AND av_content_type = "Audio"
)
SELECT
  (
    (
      (summeVideoCurrent + summeAudioCurrent) - (summeVideoPast + summeAudioPast)
    ) /(summeVideoPast + summeAudioPast)
  ) * 100 as summe_${webColor}
FROM
  vid_sum_current,
  vid_sum_past,
  audio_sum_current,
  audio_sum_past as relative_difference

IF ('$Redaktionen' = 'Sport')
THEN (SELECT NULL as summe_${webColor});
ELSE (WITH past_value as(
 SELECT
  SUM(COALESCE(m_visits,0)) AS past_sum
FROM
  Piano.total_visits
WHERE site_level2 = '${app_name}'
  AND page_chapter1 = "$page_chapter1"
  AND page_chapter2 = "Alle Kapitel 2"
  AND sendungs_id = "Alle Sendungs-ID"
    AND EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      MONTH
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
    AND EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        date
    ) = EXTRACT(
      YEAR
      from
        DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
    )
),
current_value AS (
 SELECT
  SUM(COALESCE(m_visits,0)) AS current_sum
FROM
  Piano.total_visits
WHERE site_level2 = '${app_name}'
  AND page_chapter1 = "Alle Kapitel 1"
  AND page_chapter2 = "Alle Kapitel 2"
  AND sendungs_id = "Alle Sendungs-ID"
AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
)
SELECT
  ((current_sum - past_sum) / past_sum) * 100 as summe_${webColor}
FROM
  current_value, past_value as relative_difference);

IF ('$Redaktionen' = 'Sport')
THEN (SELECT NULL as summe_${webColor});
ELSE (
  WITH past_value as(
     SELECT
      ROUND(SUM(COALESCE(m_playbutton,0))/COUNT(DISTINCT(date)),0) AS past_sum
    FROM
      Piano.av_joined_daily
    WHERE site_level2 = '${app_name}'
        AND EXTRACT(

        ) = EXTRACT(
          MONTH

        )
        AND EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            date
        ) = EXTRACT(

        )
  ),
  current_value AS (
    SELECT
      ROUND(SUM(COALESCE(m_playbutton,0))/COUNT(DISTINCT(date)),0) AS current_sum
    FROM
      Piano.av_joined_daily
    WHERE site_level2 = '${app_name}'
    AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
  )
SELECT
  ((current_sum - past_sum) / past_sum) * 100 as summe_${webColor}
FROM
  current_value, past_value as relative_difference);
ENd IF

WITH past_value as(
  SELECT
    page_impressions_unique AS past_tagesmittel
  FROM
    (
      SELECT
        SUM(page_impressions_unique) as page_impressions_unique
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.facebookInsights`
      WHERE
        profileId = ${profile_ID_FB}
        AND EXTRACT(
          MONTH
          from
            time
        ) = EXTRACT(
          MONTH
          from
            DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
        )
        AND EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            time
        ) = EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
        )
    )
),
current_value AS (
  SELECT
    page_impressions_unique AS current_tagesmittel
  FROM
    (
      SELECT
        SUM(page_impressions_unique) as page_impressions_unique
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.facebookInsights`
      WHERE
        profileId = ${profile_ID_FB}
        AND EXTRACT(
          MONTH
          from
            time
        ) = $Monat
        AND EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            time
        ) = $Jahr
    )
)
SELECT
  REPLACE(CONCAT(
    CAST(
      ROUND(
        ((current_tagesmittel - past_tagesmittel) / past_tagesmittel)* 100, 2
        ) 
      AS STRING), "%"), ".", ",")
FROM
  current_value,
  past_value as relative_difference

with impressions_by_day_old as (
  SELECT
    sum(sum_impression_day) as sum_impressions, count(n_day) as num_days, avg(ID) as ID
    FROM(
	SELECT sum(page_impressions_unique) as sum_impression_day, extract(DAY from time) as n_day, avg(profileID) as ID
	  FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.facebookInsights` 
    WHERE
		EXTRACT(MONTH FROM time) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH))
		AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH))
		AND profileID = $profile_ID_FB
    GROUP BY n_day)
),
impressions_by_day_new as (
	SELECT
    sum(sum_impression_day) as sum_impressions, count(n_day) as num_days, avg(ID) as ID
    FROM(
	SELECT sum(page_impressions_unique) as sum_impression_day, extract(DAY from time) as n_day, avg(profileID) as ID
	  FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.facebookInsights`
    WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH from time) = $Monat 
    AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr 
		AND profileID = $profile_ID_FB
    GROUP BY n_day)
),
potential_reach as (
select ROUND((impressions_by_day_old.sum_impressions/impressions_by_day_old.num_days),3) as avg_impressions_old, ROUND((impressions_by_day_new.sum_impressions/impressions_by_day_new.num_days),3) as avg_impressions_new, impressions_by_day_new.ID as ID
from 
	impressions_by_day_old
JOIN
	impressions_by_day_new
ON
	impressions_by_day_old.ID = impressions_by_day_new.ID
)
SELECT (avg_impressions_new/avg_impressions_old)-1  from potential_reach

SELECT  ROUND((new_ig.page_follows/old_ig.page_follows)-1,4) as ig_difference
	FROM ( 
		SELECT followers as page_follows, profileId, time
		FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.instagram`
		WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM time) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)) 
	AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM time) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH))
	AND profileID = $profile_ID_INSTA
	) as old_ig
	JOIN ( 
		SELECT followers as page_follows, profileId, time
		FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.instagram`
		WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH from time) = $Monat 
		AND EXTRACT(YEAR from time) = $Jahr 
		AND profileID = $profile_ID_INSTA
	) as new_ig
		ON old_ig.profileId = new_ig.profileId
  ORDER BY new_ig.time DESC
  LIMIT 1

WITH past_value as(
  SELECT
    totalInteractions as past_totalInteractions
  FROM
    (
      SELECT
        ROUND(
          SUM(
            CASE
              WHEN type = 'Reel' THEN IFNULL(totalInteractions, 0)
              ELSE IFNULL(engagement, 0)
            END
          ) / DATE_DIFF(
            LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), MONTH),
            DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1),
            DAY
          ) + 1,
          0
        ) AS totalInteractions
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.instagramInsightsOwnPosts`
      WHERE
        profileId = $profile_ID_INSTA
        AND EXTRACT(
          MONTH
          from
            time
        ) = EXTRACT(
          MONTH
          from
            DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
        )
        AND EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            time
        ) = EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)
        )
    )
),
current_value AS (
  SELECT
    totalInteractions as current_totalInteractions
  FROM
    (
      SELECT
        ROUND(
          SUM(
            CASE
              WHEN type = 'Reel' THEN IFNULL(totalInteractions, 0)
              ELSE IFNULL(engagement, 0)
            END
          ) / (
            CASE
              WHEN CURRENT_DATE() < DATE_ADD(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 7), INTERVAL 1 MONTH) THEN DATE_DIFF(CURRENT_DATE(), DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), DAY) + 1
              ELSE DATE_DIFF(
                LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), MONTH),
                DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1),
                DAY
              ) + 1
            END
          ),
          0
        ) AS totalInteractions
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.$dataset.instagramInsightsOwnPosts`
      WHERE
        profileId = $profile_ID_INSTA
        AND EXTRACT(
          MONTH
          from
            time
        ) = $Monat
        AND EXTRACT(
          YEAR
          from
            time
        ) = $Jahr
    )
)
SELECT
  (
    (
      current_totalInteractions - past_totalInteractions
    ) / past_totalInteractions
  ) * 100
FROM
  current_value,
  past_value as relative_difference

with web as (
  SELECT
    SUM(IFNULL(m_visits, 0)) as summe_web,
    LEFT(CAST(timestamp(date) AS STRING), 10) as date,
    '$Redaktionen' as redaktion
  FROM
    `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.total_visits`
  WHERE
    site_level2 = "ndr.de"
    AND ${web_redaktionen:doublequote} = page_chapter1
    AND ${Unterkapitel:doublequote} = page_chapter2
    AND "Alle Sendungs-ID" = sendungs_id
    AND date BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}')
    AND DATE('${__to:date}') -- AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
  GROUP BY
    date
  ORDER BY
    date ASC
),
app as (
  SELECT
    SUM(COALESCE(m_visits, 0)) as visits_app,
    LEFT(CAST(timestamp(date) AS STRING), 10) as time
  FROM
    Piano.total_visits
  WHERE
    site_level2 = '${app_name}'
    AND page_chapter1 = "$page_chapter1"
    AND page_chapter2 = "Alle Kapitel 2"
    AND sendungs_id = "Alle Sendungs-ID"
    AND date BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}')
    AND DATE('${__to:date}')
  GROUP BY
    time
  ORDER BY
    time ASC
)
SELECT
  summe_web as Web,
  visits_app as App,
  cast(date as STRING) as date,
  '$Redaktionen' as redaktion,
from
  web
JOIN app
ON web.date = app.time
ORDEr BY date ASC

with web as (
  SELECT SUM(IFNULL(m_visits,0)) as summe, 'yes' as joiner, "Web" as platform
  FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.total_visits`
  WHERE site_level2 = "ndr.de" AND
  ${web_redaktionen:doublequote} = page_chapter1 AND
  ${Unterkapitel:doublequote} = page_chapter2 AND
  "Alle Sendungs-ID" = sendungs_id 
  AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
),
app as (
  SELECT
  SUM(COALESCE(m_visits,0)) as summe, 'yes' as joiner, "App" as platform
  FROM
    Piano.total_visits
  WHERE site_level2 = '${app_name}'
    AND page_chapter1 = "$page_chapter1"
    AND page_chapter2 = "Alle Kapitel 2"
    AND sendungs_id = "Alle Sendungs-ID"
  AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
  )
SELECT summe, '$Redaktionen' as redaktion, platform
FROM web
UNION ALL
SELECT summe, '$Redaktionen' as redaktion, platform
FROM app

with fb as (
  SELECT
    IFNULL(
      SUM(
        page_actions_post_reactions_total_love + page_actions_post_reactions_total_wow + page_actions_post_reactions_total_haha + page_actions_post_reactions_total_sorry + page_actions_post_reactions_total_anger + page_actions_post_reactions_total_like
      ),
      0
    ) as interactions,
    LEFT(CAST(time AS STRING), 10) as time
  FROM
    `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.facebookInsights` -- as facebook
  WHERE
    profileId = $profile_ID_FB
    AND time BETWEEN timestamp('${__from:date}')
    AND timestamp('${__to:date}') -- JOIN `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles` as profiles ON (facebook.profileId = profiles.facebookID AND profiles.LRA = "$LRA")
    -- Daten des ausgewählten Zeitraums minus 1 Jahr
    -- WHERE DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR from time),EXTRACT(MONTH from time), 1) <= DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1) AND DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR from time),EXTRACT(MONTH from time), 1)  >= DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $Monat, 1), INTERVAL 12 MONTH) 
  GROUP BY
    time
  ORDER BY
    time ASC
),
ig as (
  SELECT
    ROUND(
      SUM(
        CASE
          WHEN type = 'Reel' THEN IFNULL(totalInteractions, 0)
          ELSE IFNULL(engagement, 0)
        END
      ),
      0
    ) as interactions,
    IFNULL(LEFT(CAST(time AS STRING), 10), "1970-01-01") as time
  FROM
    `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.instagramInsightsOwnPosts`
  WHERE
    profileId = $profile_ID_INSTA
    AND time BETWEEN timestamp('${__from:date}')
    AND timestamp('${__to:date}')
  GROUP BY
    time
  ORDER BY
    time ASC
)
SELECT fb.interactions as Facebook, ig.interactions as Instagram, fb.time as time
from fb join ig on fb.time=ig.time
  ORDER BY
    time ASC

with web as (SELECT SUM(IFNULL(m_av_playbacks,0)) as summe_web, LEFT(CAST(timestamp(date) AS STRING),10) as date, '$Redaktionen' as redaktion
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.av_joined_daily`
WHERE site_level2 = "ndr.de" 
AND date BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}') AND DATE('${__to:date}')
-- AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
GROUP BY date
ORDER BY date ASC),
app as (
  SELECT SUM(IFNULL(m_playbutton,0)) as summe_app, LEFT(CAST(timestamp(date) AS STRING),10) as time
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Piano.av_joined_daily`
WHERE site_level2 = "$app_name" 
AND date BETWEEN DATE('${__from:date}') AND DATE('${__to:date}')
-- AND EXTRACT(MONTH from date) = $Monat AND EXTRACT(YEAR from date) = $Jahr
GROUP BY date
ORDER BY date ASC
)
SELECT summe_web as Web, summe_app as App, web.date as time, '$Redaktionen' as redaktion
from web join app on web.date=app.time
order by time asc
